# How it works  

SRC -> AST -> IR 1 -> IR 2 -> .hexpattern

Source code is turned into AST in the first phase
The AST is then turned into flat structure with pseudo-patterns and hex patterns (IR 1)
Next step does the scope and symbol resolution to turn IR 1 -> IR 2
IR 2 is a vector of hexpatterns

